HEADWORD: Demster
<hw>Dem"ster</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Deemster</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A deemster.</def>⟦br⟧
