<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(O. Scots Law)</fld> <def>An officer whose duty it
was to announce the doom or sentence pronounced by the court.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Demulce</ent>⟦br⟧
